modName: Re-Host of Skyrim City Guard Overhaul
summary: Re-host of a removed mod, by request on r/skyrimmods.
descriptionHtml:
I did not make this mod. timonier did. timonier removed this mod, we think, and since I\'ve been asked where it went I decided to re-host it. I expect no personal benefit from this and am just trying to share his work with people who came too late to the party. If this is wrong, please let me know and I will take this down. I have no intention of profiting from this, nor do I intend to claim it as my own work.

CREDITS:

timonier for writing the work I have here

Callaghan04 for Dawnstar, Hjaalmarch, Whiterun, Windhelm, Stormcloak, Markarth, Falkreath, Solitude, Winterhold guard tartans. Link: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3359

Luddeman for Riften tartans
author: timonier
